How to use:

FOR WINDOWS: Download the windows .ZIP release, uncompress and run lease.exe or unlease.exe

FOR MAC: We will soon have a Mac App release. In the meantime follow the Linux instructions

FOR LINUX: Download the python (.py) files and run by typing 'python lease.py' or 'python unlease.py'.
Note that you need to install the pywaves and base58 libraries for this to work. To install them type 'pip pywaves' and 'pip base58'

